query: SELECT MIN(chn.name) AS voiced_char, MIN(n.name) AS voicing_actress, MIN(t.title) AS voiced_animation FROM aka_name AS an, complete_cast AS cc, comp_cast_type AS cct1, comp_cast_type AS cct2, char_name AS chn, cast_info AS ci, company_name AS cn, info_type AS it, info_type AS it3, keyword AS k, movie_companies AS mc, movie_info AS mi, movie_keyword AS mk, name AS n, person_info AS pi, role_type AS rt, title AS t WHERE t.id = mi.movie_id AND t.id = mc.movie_id AND t.id = ci.movie_id AND t.id = mk.movie_id AND t.id = cc.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = ci.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = mk.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = ci.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = mk.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND cn.id = mc.company_id AND it.id = mi.info_type_id AND n.id = ci.person_id AND rt.id = ci.role_id AND n.id = an.person_id AND ci.person_id = an.person_id AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id AND n.id = pi.person_id AND ci.person_id = pi.person_id AND it3.id = pi.info_type_id AND k.id = mk.keyword_id AND cct1.id = cc.subject_id AND cct2.id = cc.status_id AND n.gender in ('m') AND t.production_year > 2002 AND t.production_year < 2012 AND (an.name like '%k%' OR an.name like '%U%' OR an.name like '%R%' OR an.name like '%Y%') AND cn.name not like '%Focus Features%' AND cn.name not like '%STX%' AND cn.country_code in ('gl','cg','lv') AND cct2.kind in ('complete','crew','complete+verified') AND k.keyword not like '%terrorist%' AND k.keyword not like '%destiny%' AND k.keyword not like '%murdered%' AND k.keyword not like '%betrayal%' AND rt.role not like '%Erin Bates%' AND mc.note not like '%China%' AND it3.info not in ('LD additional information','LD label','death date','nick names','mini biography','genres','LD number','LD status of availablility','LD pressing plant','portrayed in','admissions','LD production country','goofs','where now','magazine cover photo','spouse','LD sound encoding','LD year','LD language','tech info','budget') AND it.info in ('interviews','magazine cover photo','death date','keywords','LD length','LD analog left','LD category','LD release date','color info','locations','tech info','admissions','weekend gross','certificates','goofs','filming dates','runtimes') AND (chn.name like '%Baby Groot%' OR chn.name like '%James Bond%') AND (pi.note like '%Mike Martin%' OR pi.note like '%Hannah Nicholas%') AND mi.info in ('Zulu','Chinese','Vietnamese','French','Indonesian','Romanian','Polish','Tagalog')
